/target
**/*.rs.bk
Cargo.lock.bak

# Vestige private memory should never live in repo (V0 stores under ~/.vestige).
# .vestige/ itself IS committed (config only); local overrides are not:
.vestige/local.toml
.env
pages-seed/

# Claude Code agent scratch — worktrees, transcripts, agent-local state.
# Pattern uses `.claude/*` (not `.claude/`) so individual files inside the
# dir are ignored, but the dir itself is traversable — required for the
# vestige-review exception below to work (gitignore can't re-include files
# inside a fully-excluded directory).
.claude/*
!.claude/skills/
.claude/skills/*
# Exception: vestige-review is a project-local skill for developing Vestige
# itself (cites this repo's CODESTYLE/CLAUDE/PRD). Track it so a fresh clone
# has it; it must NOT be shipped to .agents/ — that's only for skills meant
# to be loaded by external agents.
!.claude/skills/vestige-review/

# .agents/skills/ is an install output of `vestige skills install`.
# Bundled skills get re-written from the binary on every install; nothing
# in here should be tracked by source control.
.agents/

# Skill-creator eval workspace (skills/vestige/vestige-skills-workspace/iteration-N/)
skills/vestige/vestige-skills-workspace/
.DS_Store
